                            <comment id="15037627" author="rjernst" created="Thu, 3 Dec 2015 10:34:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;See &lt;tt&gt;update_example_solrconfigs&lt;/tt&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;dev-tools/scripts/addVersion.py&lt;/tt&gt;. The current directory it traverses underneath to find solrconfigs is &lt;tt&gt;solr/server/solr/configsets&lt;/tt&gt;. This was originally using &lt;tt&gt;solr/example&lt;/tt&gt;, but was changed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7487&quot; title=&quot;check-example-lucene-match-version is looking in the wrong place - luceneMatchVersion incorrect in 5.1 sample configs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-7487&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-7487&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
